[I] Magical shell history

[T] Atuin replaces your existing shell history with a SQLite database, and
[T] records additional context for your commands.

[U] https://github.com/atuinsh/atuin

[A] Ellie Huxtable
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/tool
[F] CROSS

[L] MIT
[V] 18.15.2

[D] ec45d43e1246d0d02ca49494a3aaee9a710503c4c29fea89e5705f23 atuin-18.15.2.tar.gz https://github.com/atuinsh/atuin/archive/v18.15.2/

cargoinstopt=
atstage cross && hook_add postmake 5 "install target/${arch_target}/*/atuin $root$bindir"
atstage native && hook_add postmake 5 "install target/*/atuin $root$bindir"
